                {
                  "name": "SCENES_README.md",
                  "type": "file",
                  "content": "# Scenes Folder\n\nThis folder contains all Unity scenes used in the project.\n\n- **Menus**: UI-related scenes\n- **Levels**: Main gameplay stages (Campaign + Bonus)\n- **Sandboxes**: Technical test scenes\n- **Cutscenes**: Cinematic scenes\n\nNaming: Level_01, Campaign_01, Sandbox_Test_Mechanic, etc."
                },
                {
                  "name": "SCENES_GUIDELINES.md",
                  "type": "file",
                  "content": "## Scene Guidelines\n\n1. Keep names short and descriptive.\n2. Use prefixes (Menu_, Level_, Sandbox_, Cutscene_).\n3. Document special lighting/mechanics in scene description.\n4. Sandbox scenes must be excluded from build.\n5. Optimize cutscenes for performance."
                }
              ]
            }
